('110', '19', '1', '', '2020-01-18 13:16:08', '93', '3344', 'ea91e5e6f9828b678617e450c53cabd74e6d4264', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":114,\"title\":\"Schumacher\\u2019s wife hides the truth about his condition\",\"alias\":\"schumacher-s-wife-hides-the-truth-about-his-condition\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Willi Weber also predicted whether Schumacher would recover from a severe head injury, after which he has been recovering for several years.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The wife of the famous former racer, seven-time world champion Michael Schumacher, who has been recovering from a severe head injury for several years, hides the truth about his health. Schumacher\\u2019s former Manager Willi Weber in an interview for a German documentary made this statement. The shooting is timed to the 25th anniversary of the first championship of the driver in Formula 1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cI know that Michael received a serious blow, but I have no idea how the recovery is going. I\\u2019d like to know how he\\u2019s doing, to shake his hand, but unfortunately, his wife Corinna refuses all my attempts. She\\u2019s probably afraid that I\\u2019ll see what\\u2019s going on with him and release the truth,\\u201d Weber said.<br \\/>He also predicted whether Schumacher would recover.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cI firmly believe that Michael will recover because he is a fighter. If there is a chance, he will take it. This cannot be the end. I pray for him and I am sure we will see him again,\\u201d Free News quoted Weber as saying.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"2\",\"created\":\"2020-01-18 13:16:08\",\"created_by\":\"93\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2020-01-18 13:16:08\",\"modified_by\":null,\"checked_out\":null,\"checked_out_time\":null,\"publish_up\":\"2020-01-18 13:16:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\