('126', '20', '1', '', '2020-01-19 12:50:01', '93', '3001', 'cc0f27af176995cecdd835477afa8fd8bc803749', '{\"id\":20,\"asset_id\":\"116\",\"title\":\"Liverpool won the Champions League, beating Tottenham\",\"alias\":\"liverpool-won-the-champions-league-beating-tottenham\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Liverpool defeated Tottenham in London and won the Champions League for the first time since 2005.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The final match of the two English clubs, held on Saturday at the Madrid stadium \\u201cMetropolitano\\u201d, ended with a victory for Liverpool with a score of 2:0. Goals were scored by Mohamed Salah (2nd minute, penalty) and Divock Origi (87th).<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>Already in the first minute of the meeting, Tottenham defender Moussa Sissoko played a hand in his penalty area, and the chief referee Damir Skomina appointed an eleven-meter kick, which Salah realized. In the 87th minute, Origi hit the goal of Hugo Lloris, setting the final score in the match.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The game began with a minute of silence in memory of the former football team of Spain Jose Antonio Reyes, who died in an accident on Saturday morning.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2020-01-18 13:18:04\",\"created_by\":\"93\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2020-01-19 12:50:01\",\"modified_by\":\"93\",\"checked_out\":\"93\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2020-01-19 12:49:17\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-01-18 13:18:04\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/2020\\\\\\/01\\\\\\/18\\\\\\/2e9cc20b-7b8c-4306-a623-7d99aadaf316.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/2020\\\\\\/01\\\\\\/18\\\\\\/2e9cc20b-7b8c-4306-a623-7d99aadaf316.jpg\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":2,\"ordering\":\"2\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"1\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', '0'),
('127', '19', '1', '', '2020-01-19 12:50:33', '93', '3490', 'b3da89919d516473ceff17f7f8fef105ff125b71', '{\"id\":19,\"asset_id\":\"114\",\"title\":\"Schumacher\\u2019s wife hides the truth about his condition\",\"alias\":\"schumacher-s-wife-hides-the-truth-about-his-condition\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Willi Weber also predicted whether Schumacher would recover from a severe head injury, after which he has been recovering for several years.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The wife of the famous former racer, seven-time world champion Michael Schumacher, who has been recovering from a severe head injury for several years, hides the truth about his health. Schumacher\\u2019s former Manager Willi Weber in an interview for a German documentary made this statement. The shooting is timed to the 25th anniversary of the first championship of the driver in Formula 1.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cI know that Michael received a serious blow, but I have no idea how the recovery is going. I\\u2019d like to know how he\\u2019s doing, to shake his hand, but unfortunately, his wife Corinna refuses all my attempts. She\\u2019s probably afraid that I\\u2019ll see what\\u2019s going on with him and release the truth,\\u201d Weber said.<br \\/>He also predicted whether Schumacher would recover.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u201cI firmly believe that Michael will recover because he is a fighter. If there is a chance, he will take it. This cannot be the end. I pray for him and I am sure we will see him again,\\u201d Free News quoted Weber as saying.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2020-01-18 13:16:08\",\"created_by\":\"93\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2020-01-19 12:50:33\",\"modified_by\":\"93\",\"checked_out\":\"93\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2020-01-19 12:50:20\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-01-18 13:16:08\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/2020\\\\\\/01\\\\\\/18\\\\\\/michael-schumachers-wife-corinna-is-hiding-the-truth-about-f1-legends-condition-says-ex-manager.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetc\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"attribs\":\"{\\\"article_layout\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_titles\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_tags\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"info_block_show_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_parent_category\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_associations\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"link_author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_create_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_modify_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publish_date\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_item_navigation\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_icons\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_print_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_email_icon\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_vote\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_hits\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_noauth\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urls_position\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"alternative_readmore\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"article_page_title\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_publishing_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_article_options\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_backend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"show_urls_images_frontend\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_image\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/2020\\\\\\/01\\\\\\/18\\\\\\/michael-schumachers-wife-corinna-is-hiding-the-truth-about-f1-legends-condition-says-ex-manager.jpg\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_article_format\\\":\\\"standard\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_audio\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_gallery\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"helix_ultimate_video\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"version\":4,\"ordering\":\"7\",\"metakey\":\"\",\"metadesc\":\"\",\"access\":\"1\",\"hits\":\"0\",\"metadata\":\"{\\\"robots\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"author\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"rights\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"xreference\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"featured\":\"0\",\"language\":\"*\",\"xreference\":\"\",\"note\":\"\"}', '0'),
('128', '18', '1', '', '2020-01-19 12:51:19', '93', '3532', '3e6eab2109dad372aa571b9ece85eb2406d59a0d', '{\"id\":18,\"asset_id\":\"112\",\"title\":\"The first molecular electronic chip containing 100 million DNA readers\",\"alias\":\"the-first-molecular-electronic-chip-containing-100-million-dna-readers\",\"introtext\":\"<p>Roswell completed the development and prototyping of the first of its kind molecular-electronic chips, which used all the latest achievements from the fields of semiconductor technology, nanotechnology, biosensors, etc. All this made it possible to create an integrated CMOS chip, which contains a huge number of elements of molecular sensors, which, at a chip price of $ 100, can read information from the entire human genome in just one hour.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>In 2019, Roswell Biotechnologies, Inc, whose management managed to attract $ 32 million of investments, completed the development of a number of key technologies necessary for implementing direct, high-speed and accurate reading of genetic data and other information of biological origin.<\\/p>\\r\\n\",\"fulltext\":\"\\r\\n<p><img src=\\\"images\\/data-reader-device.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>As mentioned above, Roswell\\u2019s first molecular-electronic chip is designed to quickly read genetic information from DNA. The chips that the company plans to create in the near future will be much more complicated and they will be able to perform more complex functions, such as detecting certain types of proteins, biomarkers of various diseases, which can be used in field infectious medicine, environmental monitoring, or to identify biological samples of various nature.<\\/p>\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2020-01-18 09:43:42\",\"created_by\":\"93\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2020-01-19 12:51:19\",\"modified_by\":\"93\",\"checked_out\":\"93\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2020-01-19 12:51:04\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-01-18 09:43:42\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",