('129', '17', '1', '', '2020-01-19 12:51:44', '93', '2931', '408b7e9b8911e1cf05e1633cf46886c2b1b2f718', '{\"id\":17,\"asset_id\":\"109\",\"title\":\"A Chinese company has created a robot cat\",\"alias\":\"a-chinese-company-has-created-a-robot-cat\",\"introtext\":\"<p>The international electronics show (CES) was held in Los Angeles, where a Chinese company presented a cat-robot that can be trained. Elephant Robotics created the new project.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The MarsCat robot is completely autonomous and can be configured. It reacts to the touch and voice of the owner and responds to the given name. He can also play with various items.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>The authors of the project are sure that Allergy sufferers and busy people who do not have the opportunity to pay much attention to a live pet will appreciate the gadget. The robot is not yet available for sale, but on the company\\u2019s website, it can be ordered for $ 700.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>MarsCat was the first Elephant Robotics product designed for home use. Founded in 2016, the company produces robots to perform functions in industrial enterprises.<\\/p>\",\"fulltext\":\"\",\"state\":1,\"catid\":\"8\",\"created\":\"2020-01-18 09:22:01\",\"created_by\":\"93\",\"created_by_alias\":\"\",\"modified\":\"2020-01-19 12:51:44\",\"modified_by\":\"93\",\"checked_out\":\"93\",\"checked_out_time\":\"2020-01-19 12:51:27\",\"publish_up\":\"2020-01-18 09:22:01\",\"publish_down\":\"0000-00-00 00:00:00\",\"images\":\"{\\\"image_intro\\\":\\\"images\\\\\\/2020\\\\\\/01\\\\\\/18\\\\\\/MarsCat-63.jpg\\\",\\\"float_intro\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_intro_caption\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"float_fulltext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_alt\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"image_fulltext_caption\\\":\\\"\\\"}\",\"urls\":\"{\\\"urla\\\":false,\\\"urlatext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targeta\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlb\\\":false,\\\"urlbtext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targetb\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"urlc\\\":false,\\\"urlctext\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"targ