('3', 'com_content.article', 'The first molecular electronic chip containing 100 million DNA readers', 'the-first-molecular-electronic-chip-containing-100-million-dna-readers', '<p>Roswell completed the development and prototyping of the first of its kind molecular-electronic chips, which used all the latest achievements from the fields of semiconductor technology, nanotechnology, biosensors, etc. All this made it possible to create an integrated CMOS chip, which contains a huge number of elements of molecular sensors, which, at a chip price of $ 100, can read information from the entire human genome in just one hour.</p>\r\n<p>In 2019, Roswell Biotechnologies, Inc, whose management managed to attract $ 32 million of investments, completed the development of a number of key technologies necessary for implementing direct, high-speed and accurate reading of genetic data and other information of biological origin.</p>\r\n', '1', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0', '1', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_image\":\"images\\/2020\\/01\\/18\\/Screen-Shot-2019-12-30-at-9.17.33-AM-730x430.jpg\",\"helix_ultimate_article_format\":\"standard\",\"helix_ultimate_audio\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_gallery\":\"\",\"helix_ultimate_video\":\"\"}', '0', '{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}', '93', '', '2020-01-18 09:43:42', '93', '2020-01-19 12:51:19', '*', '2020-01-18 09:43:42', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '18', '113', '{\"image_intro\":\"images\\/2020\\/01\\/18\\/Screen-Shot-2019-12-30-at-9.17.33-AM-730x430.jpg\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}', '{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}', '2', '3', '6', '', '', '8', '', '1'),
('4', 'com_content.article', 'Schumachers wife hides the truth about his condition', 'schumacher-s-wife-hides-the-truth-about-his-condition', '<p>Willi Weber also predicted whether Schumacher would recover from a severe head injury, after which he has been recovering for several years.</p>\r\n<p>The wife of the famous former racer, seven-time world champion Michael Schumacher, who has been recovering from a severe head injury for several years, hides the truth about his health. Schumachers former Manager Willi Weber in an interview for a German documentary made this statement. The shooting is timed to the 25th anniversary of the first championship of the driver in Formula 1.</p>\r\n<p>I know that Michael received a serious blow, but I have no idea how the recovery is going. Id like to know how hes doing, to shake his hand, but unfortunately, his wife Corinna refuses all my attempts. Shes probably afraid that Ill see whats going on with him and release the truth, Weber said.<br />He also predicted whether Schumacher would recover.</p>\r\n<p>I firmly believe that Michael will recover because he is a fighter. If there is a chance, he will take it. This cannot be the end. I pray for him and I am sure we will see him again, Free News quoted Weber as saying.</p>', '1', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0', '1', '{\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"info_block_show_title\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_associations\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_page_title\":\"\",\"show_publishing_optio